      </p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Card 1: Ploeggeest -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 p-8 text-center" data-cue="slideInUp">
          <div class="text-6xl mb-4">ğŸ¤</div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-putters-heading mb-4">Ploeggeest</h3>
